<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6209] ACL Corrections for AccessControllerProtocol apis</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6209</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;APIs provided in AccessController are authorized against global-admin permissions. Instead we need to check for table-admin level permissions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Edit: Append operation also has no authorization check. We can update it together.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
